data.description: Beautiful 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom home located in sought after Federal Hill area. Exposed brick throughout both levels of home, as well as a decorative brick fireplace. Kitchen offers wine fridge and bar perfect for hosting! The open concept main level leads to a  beautiful deck and fenced in patio area great for relaxing on those warm summer nights while star gazing. Take a short walk in any direction from this home and you're bound to find a endless possibilities for things to do and see!
